		<name>Jay's Guide to Maa</name>
		<author>Jay Ahuja</author>
		<description>This is a collection repository of 2024 additions and third party additions from several Non-WOTC sources that we have incorporated in Maa games. The new Fantastic Fletcher update is Live! Sidenote, Fixed Goddess Kaalraatri's vestige-champion weapon's additional damage. Now with Reworked Monk Class, Maarut Lineage.</description>
		<source>Jay's Guide to Maa</source>
